Package: kernstadapt
Title: Spatio-temporal adaptive kernel estimators for intensities
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jonatan A", "González", , "jonathan.gonzalez@kaust.edu.sa", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2296-5271")),
    person("Paula", "Moraga", , "paula.moraga@kaust.edu.sa", 
            role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5266-0201"))   
            )
Maintainer: Jonatan A González <jonathan.gonzalez@kaust.edu.sa>
Description: "kernstadapt" is an R package for adaptive kernel estimation of the intensity of spatio-temporal point processes. The methodology used for estimation is presented in González and Moraga (2022). <https://arxiv.org/pdf/2208.12026.pdf>.
